    "headline": "Roche launches the cobas eplex respiratory pathogen panel 3, a fast and comprehensive test to help clinicians treat patients with respiratory infections, in CE markets",
    "summary": "Roche (SIX: RO, ROP; OTCQX: RHHBY) announced today the launch of the cobas® eplex respiratory pathogen panel 3 (RP3), a new diagnostic test designed to detect a broad spectrum of viruses and bacteria that cause respiratory illness. The test is now available in countries accepting the CE mark.",
